{"type": "article", "id": 35868, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。PS：我们认为这个世界的重要性不应该有绝对的等级，重点是看得更多，探索更多。", "date": "2016-12-22T02:32:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 5, "author": 1218, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161222104138DKw1HPO79gLQVNBU.jpg", "contents": "<h3>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h3><p class=\"\"><b>1. 特朗普组建白宫国家贸易委员会</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161222093617WKR2jQm7anUhyYt6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; @视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">美国佛州棕榈滩，美国候任总统特朗普对媒体发表讲话，宣布组建白宫国家贸易委员会，并于波音公司和洛克希德马丁两家公司的 CEO 见面。</p><p class=\"\">特朗普过渡团队在声明中称：“组建国家贸易委员会显示了当选总统振兴美国制造业，让每名美国人都有机会获得体面工作和体面工资的决心。”<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>2. &nbsp;难民政策遭抗议</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161222100813sAIn6Y4Zg7Swx3e9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">德国柏林，近 200 名德国民众聚集在德国总理默克尔办公地点联邦总理府前，悼念 19 日晚柏林恐袭死难者，并高呼口号要求默克尔下台，表达对其难民政策不满。大批警察到现场维持秩序，另有部分民众到现场支持默克尔，指责游行者为新纳粹。<br></p><p class=\"\">3. <b>&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">土耳其总统接见阿勒颇“</span></b>Twitter&nbsp;<b><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">女孩”</span></b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></span></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612221033408Mvo9bi7BscT6zal.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p>土耳其总统埃尔多安发布了一张和叙利亚阿勒颇女孩 Bana Al-Abed 的合影照片。<br><br>此前，这名 7 岁女孩此前通过社交媒体 Twitter 用英文直播阿勒颇的情况，被各大媒体转载报道，同时也被部分网民质疑其真实性。</p><p class=\"\"><b>4. &nbsp;难捱的雪</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161222101612WvFGdV2lZ48wupSk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">叙利亚阿勒颇阿扎兹镇，当地普遍降雪，“帐篷城”居民生活也变得更加艰难。<br></p><h3>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h3><p class=\"\"><b>1. &nbsp;雾霾散去</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161222092621n5wMDFAL4CJ8ybNx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">北京，“红警”雾霾解除，劲风吹过，雾霾消散，标志建筑凸显。图为雾霾渐散后中国尊、财富大厦、央视新址大楼标志性建筑凸显的情形。&nbsp;<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>2. &nbsp;橘子温泉</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161222082146UrFZCyPV1dHTMLDj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; @视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">日本楢叶町，当地民众泡“橘子温泉”，该温泉是日本东北部的习俗，也是当地人自 2011 年福岛核电站泄漏后首次体验该习俗。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>3. &nbsp;圣诞老人圣诞树</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161222094602rCTINOBpyk1aRsMY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; @视觉中国&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">圣诞节临近，泰国普吉岛一家酒店内，出现了一棵由数百个不同造型的圣诞老人玩偶组成的圣诞树。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>4. 告别恐怖袭击的阴影</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612220952417A6sKubfkFdNGiCn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@视觉中国</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">德国柏林，除了 19 日发生恐袭的圣诞市场外，在 20 日停业的圣诞市场都在 21 日重新开业，节日氛围再次笼罩柏林，德国的民众也正努力走出恐袭阴影。图为柏林市中心的索尼中心广场，一名扮成冰雪女王的表演者。<br></p>"}